cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about a large-scale dataset of dashcam videos for intelligent driving and related computer vision technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of learning-based models, which suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category. The dataset is related to robotics and autonomous vehicles, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of annotations to improve learning-based models, which could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of security and privacy in collecting and using such datasets, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
